Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.70,0:22:51.78,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(250,250)}难道他今天不来追我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.78,0:22:53.72,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(250,250)}如果能够坦率一点就好了...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.64,0:22:57.30,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(350,350)}毕竟 我也是第一次知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.30,0:23:01.06,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(350,350)}这是种令人悲伤的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:02.32,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(250,250)}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.32,0:23:04.10,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(250,250)}为什么要与我背道而行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.10,0:23:05.84,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(250,250)}也不告诉我其中的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.84,0:23:08.34,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(250,350)}这真的很令人焦躁不安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.48,0:23:11.40,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(350,350)}这种话怎么说得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.40,0:23:15.14,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(350,350)}但是刚才这句不是我的心里话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:16.42,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(250,250)}告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:18.10,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(250,250)}你为什么生气了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.10,0:23:19.88,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(250,250)}是我不够可爱了吗
